  "purpose": "Slug → human display label, in 3 layers (committed defaults / per-deployment override file / runtime-editable DB rows). Manifests carry slugs ONLY. SPA reads the merged result via GET /api/navigation/api/v1/G/slug-translations. Missing slug → show slug as-is (fallback). Rename a label = edit ONE line here OR override at runtime — no manifest changes, no re-registrations. See 00_docs/platform/slug-translations-per-deployment-2026-04-28.md.",
  "owner-directive-2026-04-25": "Do NOT edit manifests for label changes. Add/edit entries here.",
  "owner-directive-2026-04-28": "Three-layer translation: this file is Layer 1 (defaults). Layer 2 = /etc/zorbit/<env>/slug-translations.override.json. Layer 3 = slug_translations_override DB table editable via /m/navigation/admin/labels by super-admins.",

